OL,3,CArrest footage shows man lying about
OL,4,Ckilling his girlfriend
OL,6,FA 41-year-old man who murdered his
OL,7,Fteenage girlfriend in Oldbury by
OL,8,Framming a truck into her is seen lying
OL,9,Fto police in body cam footage about
OL,10,Fwhat happened at the time.
OL,12,FMohammed Azim was arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of murder after calling
OL,14,Femergency services to report 19-year-
OL,15,Fold Lily Whitehouse had been injured
OL,16,Fin a hit and run in November last year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
