OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781884084
OL,3,CArrest footage shows man lying about
OL,4,Ckilling his girlfriend
OL,6,FAzim was arrested at the scene, and it
OL,7,Fwas later revealed he had been lying
OL,8,Fabout what had happened. In court he
OL,9,Fadmitted hitting Lily with his truck,
OL,10,Fbut claimed it was an accident.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Nigel Box, from
OL,13,FWest Midlands Police, said: "Within
OL,14,Ftwo minutes of the collision Mohammed
OL,15,FAzim has placed Lily back into the
OL,16,Frecovery truck, and he makes a 999
OL,17,Fcall during which he fabricates a
OL,18,Fversion of events about what happened
OL,19,Fto Lily.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781884084
OL,3,CArrest footage shows man lying about
OL,4,Ckilling his girlfriend
OL,6,F"He says that another car came along
OL,7,Fand hit Lily and ran her over causing
OL,8,Fher injuries, and had driven off.
OL,10,F"Whilst the call handler is pleading
OL,11,Fwith him to administer CPR to try and
OL,12,Fhelp Lily, Mohammed Azim doesn't help
OL,13,Fher.
OL,15,F"He stands over her on a couple of
OL,16,Foccasions and is seen to be rubbing
OL,17,Fher back, but he makes no real effort
OL,18,Fto try and save her life.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781884084
OL,3,CArrest footage shows man lying about
OL,4,Ckilling his girlfriend
OL,6,F"I believe that it was an escalation
OL,7,Fof an argument they were having. I
OL,8,Fbelieve that he is a domestic abuse
OL,9,Fperpetrator, and that this was an
OL,10,Fincident of domestic abuse, and I
OL,11,Fbelieve that he purposely and
OL,12,Fintentionally drove his vehicle at
OL,13,FLily.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
