OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781884084
OL,3,CArrest footage shows man lying about
OL,4,Ckilling his girlfriend
OL,6,F"We know that Lily had secured a flat
OL,7,Ffor herself, and she was in the
OL,8,Fprocess of gathering items which would
OL,9,Fbe used for when the baby came home,
OL,10,Fand we know from her family that she
OL,11,Fwas really excited at the prospect of
OL,12,Fbeing a young mum, and Azim took that
OL,13,Fopportunity away from her."
OL,15,FAzim was found guilty of murder on
OL,16,FFriday 19 June, and is due to be
OL,17,Fsentenced at Wolverhampton Crown Court
OL,18,Fon Monday 22 June.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/5
